Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.70,0:02:44.82,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The Great Pirate Era is experiencing
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.82,0:02:49.66,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,a groundswell\Nbeyond the World Government's expectation.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.33,0:02:58.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Being at the center of the unstoppable swell\Nand drawing the most attention is...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.59,0:03:02.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Monkey D. Luffy!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.64,0:03:05.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And the Straw Hats!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.27,0:03:12.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}In order to cope with the \Nturbulent Great Pirate Era,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.17,0:03:16.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}50 leaders hold the World Conference\Nevery four years.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.03,0:03:20.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Known as the Reverie, it is about to start.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.08,0:03:29.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The times are changing drastically now.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.21,0:03:45.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}"Going into Action!\NThe Implacable New Admiral of the Fleet - Sakazuki!"{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.89,0:03:54.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This is the Navy Headquarters led by\Nthe new Admiral of the Fleet, Sakazuki.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.22,0:03:56.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}New Marineford.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.50,0:04:00.36,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Two years ago, in the Paramount War between
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.36,0:04:03.32,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,the Navy Headquarters and \Nthe Whitebeard Pirates,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.32,0:04:05.09,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}the Navy triumphed.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.09,0:04:09.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}However, Marineford became a battleground\Nand was devastated.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.62,0:04:14.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It was long renowned as \Nthe home of "justice,"{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.58,0:04:18.57,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}but to prepare for the \Nintensifying Pirate Era, the
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.57,0:04:21.32,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,World Government built an even \Ngreater impregnable fortress.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.88,0:04:26.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The new fort of "justice" that's located\Nat the entrance of the New World...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.67,0:04:29.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That's New Marineford.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.30,0:04:32.27,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,NAVY
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.63,0:04:36.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fujitora showed up at Mariejois?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.74,0:04:38.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.77,0:04:42.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I told him that\Nhe can't set foot in any Navy base...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.17,0:04:45.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...until he brings Straw Hat and Law's heads!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.72,0:04:50.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He can't just claim to have forgotten what I said to him\Nin Dressrosa!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.93,0:04:52.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I'm scared.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.98,0:04:56.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How dare he come back! That fool!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.56,0:04:59.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yes, we all know what you told him...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.44,0:05:02.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then why didn't you send him away?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.78,0:05:06.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well... he was perfectly prepared \Nwith theoretical arguments and
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.38,0:05:07.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,we couldn't combat his wit...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.95,0:05:12.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is not a Navy base...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.04,0:05:16.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's just a quibble!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.46,0:05:18.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is he a witty monk or something?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.71,0:05:23.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.09,0:05:25.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't it a difficult job?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.97,0:05:28.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fleet Admiral...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.89,0:05:30.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,S-Sengoku-{\i1}san{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.89,0:05:34.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up, you semi-retired has-been!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.44,0:05:39.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who else has gone to Mariejois?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.02,0:05:43.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A-Admiral Ryokugyu-{\i1}san{\i0} has!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.19,0:05:45.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ryokugyu, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.11,0:05:47.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Contact him immediately!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.40,0:05:49.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir! What should I tell him?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.95,0:05:54.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's obvious!\NTell him to turn Fujitora away if he sees him!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.75,0:05:56.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All of you, go!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.29,0:05:59.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.09,0:06:04.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What a bunch of idiots!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.34,0:06:10.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't you go back to your post, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.51,0:06:15.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's strange, isn't it?\NThat Straw Hat's bounty...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.39,0:06:19.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...went up to 1.5 billion.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.02,0:06:24.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That stupid brat...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.82,0:06:29.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I should've killed him somehow at that time!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.33,0:06:44.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The hell with the Great Pirate Era...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.88,0:06:48.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On that day two years ago,\Nit was supposed to end!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.34,0:06:53.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We of the Navy thought we ended it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.56,0:07:01.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just as there are those\Nwho will inherit Roger's will,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.56,0:07:08.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,some people will inherit Ace's\Nsometime in the future!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.94,0:07:15.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if you break their blood bond,\Nyou'll never be able to extinguish their flame!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.33,0:07:22.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's how it came down unbroken\Nthroughout the ages!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.63,0:07:27.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And someday in the future,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.76,0:07:32.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,carrying hundreds of years of history\Non his shoulder,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.84,0:07:37.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,someone will fling down the gauntlet\Nin front of the world!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.35,0:07:44.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sengoku!\NYou and the World Government are afraid of...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.19,0:07:55.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...the gigantic war that will embroil\Nthe whole world in one day!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.79,0:08:08.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you see it? The tidal wave keeps growing.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.63,0:08:15.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It wasn't this large yet two years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.80,0:08:23.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But now, the tidal wave of the Great Pirate Era\Nis growing incalculably large...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.23,0:08:28.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The Paramount War took place two years ago...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.40,0:08:32.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It all started with the Whitebeard Pirates'\N2nd division commander
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.08,0:08:34.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Portgas D. Ace getting arrested{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.39,0:08:37.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}and sentenced to public execution.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.05,0:08:41.93,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,TWO YEARS AGO...\NAT THE UNDERWATER PRISON IMPEL DOWN
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.71,0:08:52.59,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The battle started in the Navy's special\NUnderwater Prison Impel Down...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.63,0:08:55.85,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It was an iron-tight stronghold\Nfrom which no one had escaped
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.85,0:08:57.41,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,for the past 20 years.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.89,0:09:02.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Detained there\Nand waiting for his execution was...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.64,0:09:04.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...Ace.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.10,0:09:07.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's my brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.44,0:09:12.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ace is my older brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.86,0:09:15.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wanna go and rescue Ace!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.66,0:09:21.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}In order to save Ace,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.62,0:09:24.90,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Luffy broke into Impel Down{\i0}\N{\i1}while the Navy
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.90,0:09:27.43,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,was distracted by Whitebeard.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.94,0:09:32.48,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,BUGGY THE CLOWN\NCHOP-CHOP FRUIT POWER-USER
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.13,0:09:32.63,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,That's what I don't like \Nabout you and Red-Haired!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.38,0:09:35.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll change my plan!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.22,0:09:39.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now for some chaos!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.60,0:09:40.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm with you!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.40,0:09:56.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Long time no see-{\i1}gane{\i0}, Straw Hat Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.24,0:09:59.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now I'm free thanks to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.47,0:10:02.31,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,MR. 3 / GALDINO\NWAX-WAX FRUIT POWER-USER
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.49,0:10:02.24,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,I always pay back my debts-{\i1}gane{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.56,0:10:07.39,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,BON CLAY\NCLONE-CLONE FRUIT POWER-USER
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.58,0:10:07.54,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,It's been a long time! Straw-{\i1}chan{\i0}, it's me!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.08,0:10:13.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Luffy gained new companions\Nwhile he made a dash to save Ace.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.09,0:10:17.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}However, Warden Magellan stood in his way.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.68,0:10:21.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you want to touch these?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.48,0:10:38.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you wanna give up now?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.78,0:10:45.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna rescue Ace
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.12,0:10:49.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and we're gonna get out of here!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.96,0:10:54.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not gonna die without even seeing him!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.96,0:10:59.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not gonna let you execute Ace!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.14,0:11:04.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's that smoke?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.01,0:11:09.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't wanna lose to you by not touching you\Nbecause you're poisonous.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.73,0:11:13.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd rather touch you and...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.44,0:11:19.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...give you my arms!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.74,0:11:23.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want your arms!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.32,0:11:26.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But if you want me to have them,\NI'll take them!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.16,0:11:30.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gum-Gum...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.46,0:11:35.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Jet Bazooka!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.16,0:12:13.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You seem to have brought me to my knees!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.21,0:12:17.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We never really know what \Na cornered rat will do!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.05,0:12:26.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But now you got enough poison on your hand...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.93,0:12:30.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...to affect your whole body!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.94,0:12:34.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hydra!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.00,0:13:01.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Give me...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.46,0:13:04.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Ace!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.31,0:13:18.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is your punishment.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.77,0:13:23.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There is no way to neutralize\Nthe amount of poison you have absorbed!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.11,0:13:27.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You will agonize for 24 hours
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.11,0:13:29.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and then pass...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.62,0:13:31.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...to the real hell!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.04,0:13:42.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A... A...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.84,0:13:44.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ace!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.03,0:14:12.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The poison passed into his system\Nand he was dying,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.01,0:14:16.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}but Emporio Ivankov, the Horm-Horm Fruit power-user,\Nsaved him.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.38,0:14:29.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Miracles only happen to people\Nwho don't give up!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.51,0:14:32.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't underestimate miracles!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.90,0:14:41.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What... What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.86,0:14:51.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Food!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.70,0:14:55.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Thus, Luffy recovered.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.33,0:15:02.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Along with Ivankov and his right arm Inazuma,\Nthe Snip-Snip Fruit power-user,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.06,0:15:04.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Luffy tried to reach Ace.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.00,0:15:06.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ace!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.34,0:15:08.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is this it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.28,0:15:10.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ace?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.97,0:15:17.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's not here!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.56,0:15:21.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And there, he met...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.77,0:15:25.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're Straw Hat Luffy, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.36,0:15:28.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Have mercy on me!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.38,0:15:32.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Take me with you!\NI can help you for sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.53,0:15:35.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}"First Son of the Sea" Jimbei.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.49,0:15:39.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They'll hand over Ace boy\Nto the Navy Headquarters at any cost!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.81,0:15:41.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You need to give up on him!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.77,0:15:44.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, you need to trust Whitebeard.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.94,0:15:49.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's not gonna give up on one of his own!\NHe'll definitely do something!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.67,0:15:51.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--I'm going!\N--Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.89,0:15:56.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna go to the Navy Headquarters!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.60,0:15:59.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be stupid!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.10,0:16:02.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.56,0:16:05.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I give up now...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.69,0:16:08.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...I'm gonna regret it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.65,0:16:13.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Straw Hat became the first intruder\Nin Impel Down's history...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.72,0:16:17.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He snuck in alone\Nbut when he came back out,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.83,0:16:20.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,he was surrounded by prisoners.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.62,0:16:25.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He even allied with\Nthose who he once fought...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.90,0:16:34.99,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,NAVY
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.39,0:16:40.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The terrible thing is whenever he \Ndoes something, miracles happen...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.10,0:16:45.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The prime example of that is\Nwhat happened at the Gates of Justice!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.86,0:16:52.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh no-{\i1}gane{\i0}! We can't open it-{\i1}gane{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.91,0:16:56.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn! It's a dead end after \Ncoming this far-{\i1}gane{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.41,0:16:58.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're talking like me-{\i1}gane{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.08,0:17:01.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--What're we gonna do, you shark?!\N--Sail through it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.67,0:17:04.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's impossible! This is a disaster!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.54,0:17:08.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How can you be so relaxed?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.42,0:17:15.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Keep firing! Sink them...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.68,0:17:21.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Gates of Justice are opening!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.10,0:17:24.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.60,0:17:26.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are the Gates opening?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.10,0:17:29.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was with him at the entrance a while ago!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.94,0:17:32.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He stayed alone at Impel Down?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.78,0:17:35.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Hey, can you hear me, Bon-{\i0}chan{\i1}?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.32,0:17:38.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Why are you doing this?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.07,0:17:41.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}We were gonna break out together,\Nweren't we?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.20,0:17:45.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How many times have I been saved by you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.79,0:17:48.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If you are there, say something,\NBon-{\i0}chan{\i1}!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.83,0:17:50.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Bon-{\i0}chan{\i1}!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.05,0:17:57.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Bon{\i0}-chan{\i1}, the Gates are closing.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.39,0:18:04.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We... have to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.56,0:18:12.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.16,0:18:25.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Brother Bon, thank you!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.29,0:18:29.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}--Thank you!\N--Thank you!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.38,0:18:35.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Straw-{\i1}chan{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.72,0:18:36.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bon-{\i1}chan{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.84,0:18:37.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Straw-{\i0}chan{\i1}!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.09,0:18:42.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You gotta save your brother at any cost!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.43,0:18:52.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I know that you can save \Nyour brother for sure!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.15,0:18:55.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bon-{\i1}chan{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.41,0:19:10.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}To take down Whitebeard\Nby luring him out with Ace's public execution,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.87,0:19:15.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}the Navy summoned the best\Nand was prepared to fight.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.32,0:19:17.78,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,NAVY
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.02,0:19:35.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have something to tell you all.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.74,0:19:39.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Portgas D. Ace...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.84,0:19:44.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's about the great significance of\Nhis death today.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.87,0:19:50.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A year and three months \Nafter the father's death,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.60,0:19:55.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the child was born with the blood of\Nthe world's most heinous man in his veins.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.80,0:20:00.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That was you!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.01,0:20:05.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your father is...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.68,0:20:07.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...the King of the Pirates -
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.81,0:20:09.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gold Roger!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.16,0:20:31.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here comes Moby Dick!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.73,0:21:00.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's been a while, Sengoku.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.78,0:21:02.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whitebeard.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.11,0:21:06.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You better tell me that my beloved son...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.34,0:21:08.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...is all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.47,0:21:30.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now it's coming!\NThe seaquake that he set up before!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.28,0:21:33.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Coming in the form of tsunami!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.69,0:21:40.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't think that our superior forces\Nwill guarantee us victory.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.92,0:21:46.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We could well fail.\NBecause that man has...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.82,0:21:51.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...the power to destroy the world!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.21,0:22:02.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Mount a counter-offensive!\N--Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.45,0:22:34.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yasakani Sacred Jewel!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.63,0:22:47.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Great Eruption!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.64,0:22:58.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It was a back-and-forth battle\Nand it became very intense.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.90,0:23:01.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And then...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.86,0:23:04.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He came...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.53,0:23:08.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ace!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.61,0:23:12.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're here for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.50,0:23:24.34,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}While the world surges \Npowerfully around Luffy,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.34,0:23:28.97,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Fujitora and a new Navy \NAdmiral turn up at Mariejois!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.49,0:23:33.22,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Meanwhile, from under the sea, \Nwith a flood of emotions,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.22,0:23:35.97,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Shirahoshi surfaces!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.97,0:23:37.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On the next episode of One Piece!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.31,0:23:40.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"The Paramount War! The Inherited \NWill of the King of the Pirates!"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.64,0:23:43.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna become the King of the Pirates!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.83,0:23:45.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.83,0:23:47.83,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,
